                          "name": "docH",
                          "fill": "#202124",
                          "content": "JVM 内存结构",
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 30,
                          "fontWeight": "800"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "H3MHG",
                          "name": "docLead",
                          "fill": "#4D514B",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "JVM 运行时数据区可以分为线程私有和线程共享两类。面试时需要能说明每个区域存放什么、何时创建、常见异常是什么。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.55,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "pgpEJ",
                          "name": "Exam Callout",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "fill": "#F7FAFF",
                          "cornerRadius": 8,
                          "stroke": {
                            "align": "inside",
                            "thickness": 1,
                            "fill": "#C8DAFF"
                          },
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 8,
                          "padding": 16,
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "rmSJJ",
                              "name": "calloutT",
                              "fill": "#174EA6",
                              "content": "面试追问",
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "800"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "P1H1i",
                              "name": "calloutS",
                              "fill": "#2F4E82",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "为什么程序计数器是唯一一个不会出现 OutOfMemoryError 的区域？",
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "500"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "SMi8p",
                          "name": "p1",
                          "fill": "#202124",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "1. 程序计数器：记录当前线程执行到的字节码行号，线程私有，占用空间很小。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 15
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "2qcOS",
                          "name": "p2",
                          "fill": "#202124",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "2. 虚拟机栈：每次方法调用都会创建栈帧，保存局部变量表、操作数栈、动态链接和返回地址。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 15
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "ulcIB",
                          "name": "p3",
                          "fill": "#202124",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "3. 堆：对象实例主要分配在堆上，是垃圾回收管理的核心区域，也是面试中最常被追问的部分。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 15
                        },
